; コボルドの砦～ゴーレム騒動・リーゼルの過去




;■リーゼルの髪飾り

;◇イベント01・店で髪飾り発見
*comb_1

; ノーラの店
@eval exp='game.itemWin.openSpecialBuyMode()'
@eval exp='game.itemWin.enabled = true'
@eval exp='game.itemWin.enabled = false'
@eval exp='game.itemWin.shopWin.setSelectingMark(game.itemWin.shopWin.buttons[1]);
@w05
[texton]
[name n=Nora f=nora_00]「New items are available～! Please take a look!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「...!」[k]
[name f=other_01]I looked at the store's limited edition shelves and saw something familiar.[k]
[テオ f=12]「T-that's Riselle's hair ornament...!」[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_01]「What? Are you interested in this hair ornament?」[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_03]「Hehheh, this is the most exquisite hair ornament we've had in stock recently! Quite a bargain! Hey, are you buying?」[k]
Apparently, Murmur had sold the hair ornament she had taken from Riselle to the store.[k]
The price tag says 200,000G. That's a high price. I wonder how much it was purchased for...[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_01]「This hair ornament costs 200,000G! So? You buying, sir?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Hey... This hair ornament is actually stolen. It's a precious memento that was stolen from one of my friends. I'd like it back.」[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_02]「S-s-stolen goods?!」[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_06]「No, you can't! This is a very valuable item that I spent a lot of money to buy! I would never give it away for free!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Do so, please.」[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_04]「No, no, absolutely not～! I don't care what you say! If you want it, you can pay me for it!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I'm sorry, I can't... 」[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_06]「If you can't pay, then you're not a customer! [r]You're hurting my business! Get out!」[k]
[textoff]
@outf
@eval exp='game.itemWin.close()'
@w05
@mu f=&'game.map.bgm'
@se f=door1
@gameon
[texton]
We had no choice but to leave the shop.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl076 f=10]「That was expensive... My hair ornament... 」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Riselle's shoulders slump in disappointment.[k]
...But it's too early to give up.[k]
This could be a good thing. There was a chance that the hair ornament would never be found again. But if it's for sale, I can buy it back.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Hold on a second.」[k]
[textoff]
@outf
@se f=door1
[texton]
I decided to go back to the store and ask the owner not to sell the hair ornament to another customer until I bought it.[k]
[name n=Nora f=nora_07]「...I understand. I'll wait for you if that's what you want.」[k]
...Just wait and see. I'll definitely buy it back someday![k]
[textoff]
@se f=door1
@gameon
[shopoff]


;◇イベント02・髪飾りを買い取る
*comb_2

; ノーラの店
[texton]
[name n=Nora f=nora_00]「Thank you very much for your purchase～.[r]
See! Buying it honestly like that was what you should have done in the first place!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
It was pricey, but I'm glad I managed to buy back Riselle's hair ornament.[k]
...Now, how shall I give it to her? A surprise might be good.[k]
[textoff]
[shopoff]




;■コボルドの砦

;◇イベント01・ライナス登場
*kobold_1

; サファイアシティ
@saveon
@w05
@bg f=0019
@fg c=マックス e=通常 f=01
[texton w=1]
[マックス f=01]「Yo! [テオ], that you?」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Oh, Max.」[k]
Upon entering Sapphire City, I ran into Max for the first time in ages.[k]
[マックス f=03]「Hey! [テオ]! You're awesome!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What?」[k]
[マックス f=03]「I heard you rescued all the Seagull Village girls that monsters stole away!」[k]
[テオ f=14]「Uh, um... 」[k]
That was the quest we did... But how did Max hear about it?[k]
[マックス f=03]「It caused quite a stir in Sapphire City! Young, unknown adventurers completed a difficult quest where many veterans had failed!」[k]
[テオ f=14]「Yes, that's right...」[k]
Well, if that's how it's being told, I'm kind of happy.[k]
After all, this will increase the prestige of our party and make our job easier.[k]
[テオ f=01]「How are things going with your party?」[k]
[マックス f=01]「Yeah, we're doing great! Maria and I are doing well! We're getting a lot of experience!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I see. That's good.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl077 f=01]「So Maria is doing well...」[k]
[マックス f=01]「See you later! You guys, do your best too!」[k]
@cl
Max left.[k]
Things are going well over there. We can't afford to slack off either.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl078 f=01]「Let's do our best too.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Ah!」[k]
Recently, Riselle has been saying more positive things. That's a good sign.[k]
Maybe things are starting to move in a good direction. Don't let this luck slip away.[k]
[？？？]「Hey! You there!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「？」[k]
@mu f=trick
@fg c=ライナス e=通常 f=52
A man suddenly called out to me.[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=52]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Um... is there something I can help you with?」[k]
The man looked at me silently with hatred in his eyes.[k]
...What? Is he trying to pick a fight with me? Did I do something to him...?[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=52]「You're the leader of [emb exp='game.party.displayName'], right?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Yes, that's right...」[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=52]「Don't get too cocky just because you finished one quest!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=51]「Listen, there are plenty of adventurers better than you! Don't be so smug!」[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=51]「You got lucky, but if you take on a job like that again you'll definitely fail!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Is he also talking about the labyrinth rescue?[k]
I don't think we're being conceited, so... why is he ranting at us?[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=51]「A beginner party like yours should only do the lowly chores! You've got to know your place! Understand?!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[男 key=ライナス f=52]「...Hmph!」[k]
@cl
The man said all he had to say and left.[k]
We stood there stunned by the suddenness of the event.[k]
[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh014 f=05]「...What was that about?」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd014 f=05]「...What was that about?」[k]
[endif]
[   if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs016 f=07]「What's wrong with him? He's just saying whatever he wants!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve015 f=07]「What's wrong with him? He's just saying whatever he wants!」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ f=08]「... (Ugh)」[k][endif]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Facing such strong hostility out of nowhere, I didn't know how to react. Who was that person in the first place?[k]
[リーゼル v=vl079 f=05]「That guy... He's the leader of Hawk Wing, I think. His name is Linus.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What?!」[k]
Does that mean he's Max and Maria's current leader?[k]
[テオ f=12]「Oh, really?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl080 f=06]「Yeah. I've seen him a few times before... He's kind of a celebrity in Sapphire City.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I didn't know the leader of Hawk Wing was like that. That's very different from what I imagined.[k]
As I recall, Hawk Wing was one of the most famous parties in Sapphire City, having resolved many difficult quests.[k]
Why did the leader do that...? Why is he so openly hostile to a new party like ours?[k]
[textoff]
@out
[townoff]


;◇イベント02・コボルド砦でライナスと会う
*kobold_2

; コボルド砦・通路
@saveon
@wait time=500 cond='WAY != "n"'
@walk turn=n cond='WAY != "n"'
@wait time=500
@fg c=ライナス f=11
[texton w=1]
[ライナス f=11]「Ah...!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「You're Hawk Wing's...!」[k]
To my surprise, I ran into the leader of Hawk Wing inside the fort.[k]
@fgf c=ライナス f=28
[ライナス f=28]「Damn... Why are you...?!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Apparently, Hawk Wing was the party contracted to do the same job.[k]
Linus turns his hostile gaze toward us, just as he did last time.[k]
We might be rivals undertaking the same job, but I can't help but feel bewildered by the blatant hatred.[k]
[ライナス f=06]「...Hey, you guys, go home now.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[ライナス f=06]「We, Hawk Wing, will do all the work this time. There's nothing for you to do.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I don't know what to say...」[k]
@fgf c=ライナス f=51
[ライナス f=51]「When newbies like you hang around, you just get in the way! Don't you understand that?!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Huh...!」[k]
I'm here on official business. I don't deserve to be told that.[k]
[テオ f=05]「I have to finish what I've been asked to do by the client. I'm sorry, but I can't leave.」[k]

[   if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs017 f=07]「Yes! What gives you the right to say that?!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve016 f=07]「Yes! What gives you the right to say that?!」[k]
[endif]
[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh015 f=07]「You have no right to say that!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd015 f=07]「You have no right to say that!」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg009 f=08]「We're not... We're not leaving...!」[k][endif]

@fgf c=ライナス f=06
[ライナス f=06]「...Hmph, stubborn fools.」[k]
[ライナス f=05]「Well, do whatever you want. But if you get in our way, we won't tolerate it. Remember that.」[k]
@cl
After saying this, Linus walked away as if ignoring us.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]

[   if exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve017 f=07]「What the hell is wrong with him? He really pisses me off!」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs018 f=07]「What the hell is wrong with him? He really pisses me off!」[k]
[endif]
[   if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd016 f=07]「That guy's so rude!」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM'][リム v=vh016 f=07]「That guy's so rude!」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ f=08]「...! ∗glare∗」[k][endif]

The members of our group are angered by Linus' outspokenness.[k]
@fg c=マリア e=通常 f=13
[マリア v=va105 f=13]「Sorry! I'm really sorry, guys!」[k]
; ↑ 慌てた様子でライナスに替わって謝るマリア
[テオ f=05]「...Maria!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl081 f=05]「Maria...」[k]
Maria suddenly appeared. It seems she's accompanying Linus as a member of his party.[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=14
[マリア v=va106 f=14]「I'm sorry, our leader is a little weird! He said something unreasonable, didn't he?」[k]
Maria tries to calm us down in a whisper.[k]
[マリア v=va107 f=14]「...He's not doing so well at work lately, and he's a little frustrated. So I hope you can forgive him.」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=04
[マリア v=va108 f=04]「I'll tell you later, so please don't hold it against me too!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「O-okay... If you insist... 」[k]
It wouldn't do us much good to challenge him. We shouldn't make a big deal out of it, and concentrate on completing the quest.[k]
[ライナス f=51]「Hey! Maria! What are you doing there? Let's get the hell out of here!」[k]
@fgf c=マリア f=03
[マリア v=va109 f=03]「Yes, I'm coming!」[k]
; ↑ 遠くのライナスに返事
@fgf c=マリア f=02
[マリア v=va110 f=02]「Well, I'll be going. See you later, Riselle!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl082 f=06]「U-uh, yeah. See you later.」[k]
@se f=footstep2
@clf
Maria hurriedly ran to Linus. Riselle stared dumbfounded at Maria.[k]
...Maria seems to be having a tough time.[k]
Come to think of it, it's been a long time since I sent Maria and Max on that deployment. I wonder if they are getting paid properly?[k]
I sent them for the high salary, but I hope she isn't overworking herself for it...[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント03・バリケードの前で立ち尽くすライナスたち
*kobold_3

; コボルド砦・詰め所の前
@saveon
@wait time=500'
@walk move=e cond='game.party.curX != 2'
@walk turn=s
@wait time=500
@fg l=ライナス f=28 b
@fg r=マックス e=通常 f=09
[texton w=1]
[ライナス f=28]「Damn...! How do I get in...?!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Ah...!」[k]
When I went upstairs, I encountered Linus and his group standing frustrated in front of the door.[k]
[ライナス f=28]「Those kobolds... They've barricaded themselves in. What a bunch of clever little bastards.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Apparently, that door won't open. Is that the Kobolds' base?[k]
[ライナス f=51]「Hey, Max! Come on, open the door! You're a thief after all!」[k]
[マックス f=09]「Even if you say that, there's nothing I can do if it's been barricaded... 」[k]
[ライナス f=52]「Tch...!」[k]
@cl
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
If even Max can't open it... I'd better look for another route...[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント04・コボルドリーダーと戦闘
*kobold_4

; コボルド砦・詰め所
@wait time=500
@walk turn=w cond='WAY != "w"'
@wait time=500 cond='WAY != "w"'
@fg l=kobold_black left=250 top=80 b
@fg c=kobold_red left=450 top=80 b
@fgf r=kobold_black left=650 top=80
[texton]
[name n=Kobold]「Hey, who are you guys?! What are you doing here?!」[k]
I jumped down from the roof into the room and found myself in a place packed with elite Kobolds.[k]
[name n=Kobold]「You must be adventurers from Sapphire City! Pretty stupid of you to jump right in here though. We'll turn you into pin cushions!
 
 」[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; コボルドリーダーたちと戦闘
@monster pos=1 name=シニアコボルド
@monster pos=2 name=シニアコボルド
@monster pos=3 name=シニアコボルド
@monster pos=4 name=シニアコボルド
@monster pos=5 name=シニアコボルド
@monster pos=9 name=シニアコボルド
@monster pos=10 name=コボルドリーダー
@monster pos=11 name=シニアコボルド
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false
; 勝利

@wait time=500
@treasure item=金のヘッドバンド
[if exp='! game.isFreeMode']
	[texton]
	[テオ f=01]「Okay, I got the gold headband!」[k]
	We managed to beat Linus and the others to it. Let's take this to the client in Sapphire City.[k]
	[textoff]
[endif]
@eval exp='o.コボルド退治.flag = 1'
@addevent map=ランドン渓谷・崖上 num=12 cond='! game.isFreeMode'
@addevent name=サファイアシティ num=4 cond='! game.isFreeMode && game.findItem(o.ムーンストーンの魔石) === void'
[textoff]
[eventoff]


;◇イベント05・ホークウインド襲撃
*kobold_5

; コボルド砦の外の森の中
@saveon
@wait time=500 cond='WAY != "s"'
@walk turn=s cond='WAY != "s"'
@wait time=500
@mu f=eerie
@fg l=bladesman_red left=300 top=80 b
@fg r=archer_purple left=600 top=36
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「Ah...!」[k]
Two female adventurers stood in front of our party.[k]
As I recall, these girls are Linus' party members...[k]
The girls look at us with strangely nervous faces.[k]
[テオ f=10]「Oh, what do you want from us?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_06]「...Please give us the gold headband.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「Just give us the gold headband and we won't do anything.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
...I see. So they want to steal the credit for our work. Linus must have told them to. How despicable...![k]
[テオ f=05]「...That was the result of all of our hard work. I can't give it to you.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_06]「...Couldn't you please give it to me?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「We needn't have got rough with you if you'd complied, but I've got no choice.」[k]
The two draw their weapons and confront us.[k]
...It's a messy situation. I'd rather not fight if I can help it...[k]

[   if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh017 f=07]「Captain! Let's fight! We can't be cowards!」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd017 f=07]「Captain! Let's fight! We can't be cowards!」[k]
[endif]
[   if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs019 f=07]「I will fight! We have no reason to give in!」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve018 f=07]「I will fight! We have no reason to give in!」[k]
[endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg010 f=08]「Captain... I will fight...!」[k][endif]

[リーゼル v=vl083 f=07]「Captain, I don't want to give in to this kind of... I'll fight...!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle... Guys...! I'll fight...!」[k]
Everyone is motivated. I can't possibly retreat from this.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...All right. Let's fight, guys!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_06]「Damn...!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「You insist on fighting? Then we'll just beat you!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Let's go!」[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; 女性冒険者たちと戦闘
@eval exp='game.curTeam = o.ホーク・ウイング'
@monster pos=2 name=グラディエイター
@monster pos=4 name=シューター
@anime_duel_net visible=true
@eval exp='game.inDuelBattle = true'
@callbattle bgm=boss escape=false gameover=true
@anime_duel_net visible=false
@anime_duel_sign visible=false
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery(true)'

; 戦闘に勝利
@command type=long title="<y>You <p>win<y>! What do you request from the<r>other party?"
@select text="Take their money" target=*_demand_money
@select text="Receive 10 items" target=*_demand_items
@select text="Order a 90-day suspension" cmdcond='false'
@select text="Demand rival member" cmdcond='false'
@select text="Return a friend" cmdcond='false'
[s]

; 金銭奪取
*_demand_money
[texton]
@se f=coin
@eval exp='game.party.gold += 103400'
[nw][b]Took 103,400G from the other party![/b][/nw][k]
[textoff]
@jump target=*_demand_end

; アイテム奪取
*_demand_items
[texton]
[nw][b]Took the other party's items![/b][/nw][k]
@treasure item=ふっくらパン,ふっくらパン,はちみつパン,りんご,カトラス,ロングボウ,レンジャーブーツ,革の手袋,赤いブラ,赤いパンツ
[textoff]
; シナリオに戻る
*_demand_end

@mu f=eerie
[texton w=0]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_05]「Eek...!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_05]「Strong...!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Well, we'll be going.」[k]
We easily fought them off. They had lost the duel, and were now sprawled on the ground, unable to move.[k]
...They were weaker than I expected. Are these girls really members of Hawk Wing, one of the best parties in Sapphire City?[k]
[テオ f=05]「Hey, you two.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_05]「...What?!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_05]「Hey, what are you going to do with us?!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I won't do anything. But I do have a question I'd like to ask you.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_05]「...Yes?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Why did you want to steal the credit for our work?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「Because that's what Linus ordered.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...I'm sorry, but I don't think the two of you were up to the task. You weren't strong enough.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_05]「Damn...!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「It's frustrating, but you're right... We are weak.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I don't understand Linus' intention in sending adventurers like you to challenge us. If he really wanted to take the credit, why didn't he send stronger warriors? 」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「...Because we are the strongest ones, even so!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「Even if we're outmatched, there was no one else.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「There are only inexperienced adventurers like us in Hawk Wing now. We're not the party we used to be.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Hey...!」[k]
I can't believe that Hawk Wing, renowned as a first-class party, was in such a state...[k]
[テオ f=05]「Then why didn't Linus himself challenge us to a fight instead of sending you? There's no point in demanding a fight you can't win.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「Linus is weaker than us.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「He's an adventurer who can only do a little bit of alchemy magic. He'd probably be no match for you.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「Originally, Hawk Wing was a party that kept its strength through the power of money. Now it can't even sustain that... 」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「In the past, Hawk Wing was a competent and excellent party, even if Linus himself wasn't such an great adventurer.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「However, we were fortunate in that he paid well and had a policy of hiring good adventurers regardless of gender, so we attracted many excellent female adventurers.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「The general perception is that men are more useful as adventurers, but there are excellent women as well!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「With more of these women in the party, Hawk Wing was able to achieve results!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「Accomplishing one difficult task after another, the party's reputation grew rapidly.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「The improved reputation attracted even better adventurers, and soon Hawk Wing became one of the best parties in the kingdom!」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I see...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「However, Linus made a major error in judgment a few months ago.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What's that...?」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「He changed the party code. He abused his leadership privileges and made it a party rule that female members were to serve as his bed partner!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What...?!」[k]
Why add such an absurd rule to the party code...?![k]
The party code is a set of rules that party members must follow. Each party has its own set of rules.[k]
The party code is absolute. No matter what the circumstances, the members must obey it. Otherwise the party could be in danger of falling apart in an emergency, due to lack of control.[k]
To maintain that control, only the leader has the privilege of setting the rules of the party.[k]
To achieve its objectives, the group must act consistently. To do so, guiding rules must be established only by the will of one person.[k]
The leader uses the code to create the party he or she envisions, and those who agree with it join the party as members... This is how an adventuring party should be.[k]
However... Unfortunately, there is no shortage of leaders who abuse that privilege.[k]
No matter how much members may disagree with the rules, they have no choice but to obey them as long as they belong to the party. Unscrupulous leaders know this and set unreasonable demands as their code.[k]
Many adventurers who are still in a weak position, such as novice adventurers, have a hard time joining a good party. Bad leaders take advantage of that and make rules that exploit them.[k]
...But of all things, to be forced to be a sexual partner...[r]
It is appalling, but since he is the leader of the group, no one can prevent him from doing so.[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「...I also told him not to add that kind of rule, but Linus didn't listen to me.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「With the establishment of the rule, women in Hawk Wing had to submit to his sexual demands. As a result, female members who couldn't tolerate the new code quit one by one.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「The better members were the first to leave, so the only ones left were the less capable members like us... Naturally, we were no longer able to achieve the same results as before, and our party quickly lost power.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「...Adventurers who want to make a name for themselves by belonging to a prominent party still volunteer to be a part of it, so we're currently still able to maintain the appearance of a first-class party!」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「However, there's no substance to it, just past achievements. In time, it will become a third-rate party in both reputation and reality.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
A party with no real ability to repeat past glories...[k]
I couldn't tell from the original request, but Hawk Wing must have had a serious shortage of people. Now I understand why they tried to hire temporary adventurers at the bar with unbeatable rates.[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「Hawk Wing no longer has the power it once had. However, despite its decline, Linus was once the head of a party that enjoyed great fame... 」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「He's got a lot of pride and really thinks he's special. You and your rising star party must be a great distraction for him.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I see... So that's why he's always so hostile to us...[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_01]「He's quite willing to use any means to achieve his goal. Please be careful not to provoke him too much... 」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Okay, I'll be careful.」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=bladesman_red_00]「So, it's time for us to go... 」[k]
[女性冒険者 f=archer_purple_07]「Well then... 」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thanks for telling me about it. Take care.」[k]
Exactly 30 minutes after the duel, the girls, now able to move, walked quietly away.[k]
I see... I understand Linus more now.[k]
I can't say I like it, but if he's a problematic person, there's no point feeling bad about it each time he berates me. Let's get on with our own adventure.[k]
I'm more worried about Max and Maria, who Linus hired as temps. I hope he isn't making unreasonable demands or anything...[k]
[textoff]
@fa
[eventoff bgm]


;◇イベント06・ムーンストーンの魔石
*kobold_6

; サファイアシティ
@jump storage="free02.scn" target=*kobold_6 cond='game.isFreeMode'
@saveon
@wait time=500
[texton w=1]
@fg c=シュバルツ f=00
[シュバルツ f=01]「Hey, [テオ].」[k]
I ran into Mr. Schwarz just as I was returning to town.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Ah, Mr. Schwarz. It's been a while.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「How's the adventure going? Actually, I have something for you.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Something for me?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「Here. It's one of the ones you're looking for.」[k]
[name f=other_06]Saying this, Mr. Schwarz handed me a shiny jewel.[k]
[テオ f=12]「This is...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「It is a Moonstone, one of the 12 magical stones. I talked to a friend of mine who gave it to me for free.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「The Moonstone magic stone...」[k]
[name f=other_06]It was a magic stone that emitted a white light. It radiated a different kind of brilliance and magic power than the Emerald Magic Stone.[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「[テオ], take it.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Is that okay?」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You intend to summon the god Polaris and defeat the devil, right? So of course you should have this stone.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you, Mr. Schwarz!」[k]
@getitem item=ムーンストーンの魔石
[シュバルツ f=01]「Keep collecting the rest of the magic stones. Good luck, [テオ].」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「See you next time.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
[texton w=0]
Alright! Now we have two magic stones![k]
It's going quite well. There are 10 left. We still have a long way to go, but we'll do our best to collect them.[k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]




;■悪魔のゴーレム騒動

;◇イベント01・ゴーレムが動き出す
*golem_1

; サファイアシティ
@wait time=500
[texton]
[テオ f=02]「Well, now that the quest is over, let's take a break at the inn.」[k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='game.view.setFocusToSpot(o.冒険者の宿)'
@wait time=500
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery()'
@eventsleep keepblack=true
@wait time=2000
