@eval exp='o.サファイアシティ.bgm = "crisis"'
@gameon
@mu f=crisis
@se f=door1
@wait time=500
[texton]
When I left the inn, the town's soldiers were rushing around everywhere.[k]
[テオ f=05]「I'm sorry, what's going on?」[k]
[name n=Townsperson]「The Golem! The Golem has moved!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[name n=Townsperson]「Did you know that [b]just outside the southeast gate of the town[/b] there is a metal golem that was immobile due to a seal?」[k]
[name n=Townsperson]「It's starting to move! The seal has been broken and no one can stop it! Now it's trying to break down the town walls!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What the...!」[k]
A golem is a giant puppet with no will of its own. It is difficult to stop even with a few strong warriors. Such a troublesome thing is on the rampage...?![k]
If the walls are breached, the golem will enter the town. If that happens, we're in big trouble...![k]
[textoff]
[eventoff]


