[テオ f=12]「This is...!」[k]
Outside the town, there was a huge golem, its metal fists relentlessly punching the wall.[k]
It's trying to destroy it to invade the town![k]
The town's soldiers were attacking the golem in an attempt to stop it, but it didn't seem to be working at all.[k]
[textoff]
