A Golem has no desires of its own. So if it's moving, it must be following someone's orders. Who in the world is it, and for what purpose?[k]
@st
[？？？ v=vm074 key=ムールムール buf=13]「Gahahahaha!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, I heard a familiar voice behind me.[k]
[textoff]
@clf
