[ムールムール v=vm075 f=03]「Gahahahaha! You can't even put a scratch on a metal golem, no matter how much you try～!」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Her...!」[k]
It's that demon yet again! Perhaps she is the golem's master...[k]
...So, if we can do something about her, it might stop the metal golem.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Come on, guys, let's go!」[k]
[リーゼル f=08]「... ∗nod∗」[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk move=s
@walk move=s
@walk move=s
@wait time=500
