[texton w=1]
We rushed towards Murmur.[k]
A few soldiers who probably tried to fight Murmur were lying on the ground around her.[k]
[ムールムール v=vm076 f=03]「Gahahahaha! More, more!」[k]
[テオ f=07]「You again! Causing more trouble! I won't forgive you!」[k]
@fgf c=悪魔 f=05
[ムールムール v=vm077 f=07]「Huh? You again?! Honestly, you're so persistent!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「I won't let you get away with it today!」[k]
@fgf c=悪魔 f=07
[ムールムール v=vm078 f=07]「Huh? What are you saying? That's so annoying!」[k]
@fgf c=悪魔 f=02
[ムールムール v=vm079 f=02]「Oh well. It's a good opportunity for me to kill you all. My power has returned to normal.」[k]
@fgf c=悪魔 f=15
[ムールムール v=vm080 f=15]「Let me show you the true horror of a devil... The horror of my Breath of Death!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Breath of Death...? What?」[k]
[name n=Soldier]「Hey! Stop, leave it alone! That demon is too dangerous!」[k]
The soldier who had collapsed behind me looked up and frantically called out to me.[k]
[テオ f=05]「What do you mean?」[k]
[name n=Soldier]「She uses terrible magic! The power of her curse will kill you all!」[k]
[テオ f=12]「The power of her curse...?!」[k]
Maybe that's what she meant by death breath?[k]
I was able to repel Murmur's previous attack with my demon hunter power. However, I don't know if it can prevent that so called death breath.[k]
[name n=Soldier]「Guys! Get out of here! We're gonna get killed!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm081 f=15]「Gahahaha! Too late! I've already decided that I'm going to kill you all.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「Damn...!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm082 f=15]「Die! You annoying bugs!」[k]
[textoff]
