@monster pos=3 name=悪魔
@callbattle bgm=devil gameover=true escape=false stopbgm=true
@delevent
@addevent num=5
; 戦闘勝利
@saveon

[texton w=0]
[ムールムール v=vm083 f=28]「Damn... This is impossible...! I can't believe my Breath of Death doesn't work...! Who the hell are you?!」[k]
[ムールムール v=vm084 f=17]「Damn... Damn... Gghh!」[k]
@se f=dosa
@quake time=500 hmax=5 vmax=0
Murmur spat out a lot of blood and then stopped moving.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Did we... beat her?」[k]
We finally defeated the demon. She died before our eyes.[k]
[if exp='HUM'][リム v=vh018 f=03]「You did it! Captain!」[k][endif]
[if exp='ELF'][クレア v=ve019 f=01]「You did it! You finally defeated the devil!」[k][endif]
[if exp='DWA'][フレデリカ v=vd018 f=03]「It's amazing～ Defeating that demon!」[k][endif]
[if exp='GNO'][ミューズ v=vg011 f=22]「Captain... Amazing... 」[k][endif]
[if exp='SYL'][マルエット v=vs020 f=15]「We did it! Nice work, we did it!」[k][endif]
[リーゼル v=vl084 f=01]「Captain...!」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Riselle... Guys...! We did it, finally!」[k]
Our party rejoices in the great accomplishment of defeating a devil. We finally did it.[k]
[textoff]
@se f=rockdrop
@quake time=500
@wq
@wait time=500
@se f=rockdrop
@quake time=500
@wq
@wait time=500
@mu f=crisis
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「...! (Ah!)」[k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk turn=n
@wait time=500
[texton]
Yes, now isn't the time to bask in the afterglow of victory.[k]
The larger problem remains. The metal golem is still continuing its attack on the city walls.[k]
It shows no sign of stopping, even after the demon that was giving it orders ceased to breathe. Perhaps it's gone completely out of control.[k]
During the battle with the demon, the metal golem had moved on to attacking the town gate. Maybe it decided that would be easier to destroy.[k]
The relentless attacks were opening holes in the walls that would allow the golem to pass through, in a matter of time.[k]
If it enters the town, people will get hurt. We have to stop it as soon as possible...![k]
But how? Normal attacks don't work on metal golems.[k]
[name n=Soldier]「Waaah!」[k]
Soldiers are desperately trying to stop the metal golem, but their attacks just bounce right off.[k]
What should we do?! Is there any way to stop it?![k]
[textoff]
