[texton]
Okay, we've defeated the metal golem![k]
[リーゼル v=vl085 f=01]「Well done, Captain.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah! Nice work, guys!」[k]
Riselle's voice made me confident in my reply.[k]
Not only did we defeat that demon, we were able to destroy the golem and save the town from crisis.[k]
It is truly an accomplishment. We had worked hard to become full-fledged adventurers, and we had finally accomplished a great task.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@wait time=500

; サファイアシティ
@eval exp='game.view.close()'
@eval exp='game.openTownView(o.サファイアシティ)'
@gameon
@mu f=city
[texton]
[name n=Fiona f=fiona_00]「You have done very well. You saved our town.」[k]
Princess Fiona personally invited our party to the castle and praised us for eliminating the threat.[k]
[テオ f=02]「What stirring words. I am honored beyond measure.」[k]
[name n=Fiona f=fiona_00]「This is my way of saying thank you. Please continue to serve Sapphire City!」[k]
[textoff]
@getitem gold=200000
[texton]
[テオ f=02]「Thank you, Princess.」[k]
[name n=Fiona f=fiona_01]「You are the pride of Sapphire City. I am looking forward to your future activities!」[k]
[textoff]

@wait time=500
@fg c=シュバルツ f=02
[texton w=1]
[シュバルツ f=01]「You did it, [テオ]. You finally finished off that devil.」[k]
Mr. Schwarz, who had heard the rumors, came to talk to us.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Mr. Schwarz...!」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「You have proven you are worthy of your demon hunter lineage. Congratulations!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Thank you very much. It's an honor.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=01]「By the way, what are you going to do now?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I've decided to stop searching for magic stones for the time being, but I will continue to be an adventurer of course. My goal is to become an adventurer who surpasses my father.」[k]
[シュバルツ f=02]「I see. You can do it. Do your best. I'll be rooting for you.」[k]
[textoff]
@cl

