;■リーゼルの過去

;◇イベント01・リーゼルとの会話
*liesel_1

; 宿屋・夜
@saveon
@bg f=0001
@mu f=guild
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常 f=02
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=通常 f=02]「Are you used to this party yet?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl086 f=04]「……Yeah!」[k]
Riselle responded to my question with a carefree smile.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl087 f=01]「To be honest, at first I was really worried about whether I would be able to get along with anyone other than Maria...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl088 f=04]「But I'm having fun now. You're kind, and everyone else is nice, so...」[k]
Riselle laughed a little shyly.[k]
[テオ f=02]「I see. That's good.」[k]
Apparently Riselle had been bullied by her previous party, so she was probably worried about joining another.[k]
It's good that she's doing well now. I have the other girls in the party to thank.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl089 f=29]「H-hey, Captain...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Hmm?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl090 f=29]「I may be a hindrance right now, but I'll work hard and get stronger... so...!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl091 f=33]「I want to stay in this party forever... Because I love it here...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Oh, of course! I wouldn't leave you out of the party! Absolutely not!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl092 f=25]「Really?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I made a promise with Maria, so there's no way I'd do something like that. So don't worry.」[k]
[リーゼル f=25]「...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl093 f=03]「Thank goodness... I'm glad...」[k]
She smiled with relief to hear my words.[k]
Maybe she was treated so badly in her previous party that she doesn't want to leave one where she feels safe.[k]
Anyway, there was no way I was going to let go of Riselle, given how I feel about her.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
I wonder what she thinks of me.[k]
It seems like she trusts me to some extent, but what about as a man...?[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
@moveheart her=リーゼル guy=テオ num=5
[hoteloff]


;◇イベント02・リーゼルとの会話
*liesel_2

; 宿屋・夜
@saveon
@bg f=0001
@mu f=guild
@fg c=リーゼル e=通常 f=02
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=通常 f=02]「Well, it's getting late, so I'll go to bed soon.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl094 f=01]「That's right... Captain, I want to get changed, so could you please look away...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Oh, I'll go out until you finish changing.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl095 f=01]「It's cold outside, right? Stay there, I won't be long...」[k]
[テオ f=25]「G-got it.」[k]
@cl
I turned my back to her and heard the sound of fabric rustling from behind me.[k]
[テオ f=26]「...」[k]
Ugh... I'm nervous... I wonder if Riselle's in her underwear right now...[k]
@se f=door1
∗bang!∗[k]
[テオ f=25]「...!」[k]
@fgf c=リーゼル e=スカートとブラのみ f=25
[リーゼル v=vl096 f=25]「Kya!」[k]
Suddenly, the door to the room slammed open![k]
[name n=Men f=guy1_01]「Ahh! I drank so much!」[k]
[name n=Men f=guy2_01]「We have to get up early tomorrow, so let's get to bed!」[k]
To my surprise, several strangers opened the door and came inside![k]
Behind me, Riselle was only in her bra and skirt. I quickly stood in front of the men to hide her.[k]
[name n=Men f=guy1_01]「...Wait, what? This isn't our room.」[k]
[name n=Men f=guy2_01]「Oops, I got the wrong room. Sorry, sorry.」[k]
The men hurriedly try to leave the room. It seems they made a mistake. What a nuisance...[k]
[name n=Men f=guy1_01]「I embarrassed your cute girlfriend! I'm so sorry!」[k]
[name n=Men f=guy2_01]「Sorry to interrupt your fun!」[k]
With that, the men light-heatedly apologized and then left.[k]
[テオ f=26]「...」[k]
[リーゼル f=30]「...」[k]
...They seem to have thought Riselle and I were in a romantic relationship. I didn't mind, but she may not have liked it...[k]
[テオ f=33]「Hahaha... do we really look that way...?」[k]
Partly out of embarrassment, I laughed and said that to try and cover it up.[k]
@fg c=リーゼル f=26
[リーゼル f=26]「...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl097 f=25]「Hey, Captain, is there someone you like?」[k]
[テオ f=25]「Huh?!」[k]
