[テオ e=通常 f=01]「You've already learned level 4 magic! That's amazing, Riselle!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl102 e=通常 f=06]「Y-yeah...」[k]
If you can cast level 4 spells, that makes you a pretty capable mage.[k]
Even in guilds, mages are often required to be at least level 4 in order to be scouted. In other words, it's seen as proof of a full-fledged mage.[k]
[テオ f=02]「You really do have a talent for magic! You're definitely not useless!」[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Huh...? Riselle?」[k]
